Fetched ExtraHop CLI artifacts
------------------------------

The excli binaries are not committed to or redistributed by this repository.
Upstream ExtraHop/agent-cli grants no redistribution rights, so instead of
bundling the binaries this project pins an upstream source in
vendor/excli/source.env (EXCLI_REPO, immutable EXCLI_COMMIT, EXCLI_VERSION) and
fetches the architecture-matched release at build/install time, verifying it
against the committed vendor/excli/excli_<version>_checksums.txt trust anchor
before use. The pinned commit records the exact upstream source and retrieval
point. See docs/THIRD-PARTY-PROVENANCE.md and docs/EXCLI_MAINTENANCE.md.
